<HEADLINE>
IN FINAL YEAR 2000 TESTING, FOCUS IS ON SMALLEST FLAWS 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Calif., Conn., Mass.)   (ADDS first name and background of Burgess seven grafs from end) 
 (nk) 
 By BARNABY J. FEDER    
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   WALTHAM, Mass. _ The strings of letters and numbers flashing on
his computer screen were unintelligible to Kishore Parwani, but he
