<HEADER>
A2923 &Cx1f; tab-z
r k BC-PANAMA-PANDORA-BOX-EC     12-18 0936
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-PANAMA-PANDORA-BOX-ECONOMIST-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
U.S. IS RIGHT TO RETURN PANAMA CANAL _ BUT KEEP AN EYE ON IT  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Commentary Editors)   (This excellent 700-word ``separate-buy'' article is from the
current (week beginning 18 Dec. 1999) ECONOMIST magazine.)  
  
