<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-12-18 19:40 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2942 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s BC-FBN-SUNDAY-MOVIE-NYT &LR;      12-18 1252
