<HEADER>
A3240 &Cx1f; taf-z
r a BC-NATIONAL-SLUGLIST-CLO     12-18 1753
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-NATIONAL-SLUGLIST-CLOSER </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
